OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FCiting broken political promises and
OL,8,Fthe soaring cost-of-living, people in
OL,9,Fthe Highlands of Scotland have told
OL,10,FITV News they are frustrated with the
OL,11,Fpace of change to their quality of
OL,12,Fliving.
OL,14,FWith just days to go before Scotland
OL,15,Fheads to the polls to elect a new
OL,16,FGovernment, some voters believe none
OL,17,Fof the political parties on the ballot
OL,18,Fpaper have what it takes to deliver
OL,19,Ffor rural communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
