OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FOn the east coast of the Highlands
OL,8,Flies Dornoch, an historic royal
OL,9,Fborough, with a heavy reliance on
OL,10,Ffarming and tourism to keep the
OL,11,Feconomy going.
OL,13,FAt Davochfin Farm, Rob and Emma Smith
OL,14,Fare bringing up their young children
OL,15,Fwhile rearing cows and sheep.
OL,17,FThey've future-proofed their business
OL,18,Fby opening their farm to visitors and
OL,19,Foffering recreational experiences like
OL,20,Ffishing, golfing and camping onsite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FTraditional ways of farm life are no
OL,8,Flonger enough to pay their bills.
OL,10,F"We'll pay on average about #600 or
OL,11,F#700 a month on our electricity bill,"
OL,12,FRob told us. "Everything's far too
OL,13,Fexpensive.
OL,15,F"Everything's against you as a
OL,16,Fbusiness. As soon as you do make more
OL,17,Fmoney, everything goes up again, so
OL,18,Fyou can't win."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@fO]tD@NOUwD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
