SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FWith a plethora of promises from
OL,8,Fsparring parties, Rob said he is not
OL,9,Fconvinced by any of them.
OL,11,FThe SNP, who have strong support in
OL,12,Fthe area, announced in their manifesto
OL,13,Fthey would cap the cost of essential
OL,14,Ffood items, which angered farmers and
OL,15,Fproducers who argue they are already
OL,16,Fmaking losses on some agricultural
OL,17,Fproduce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
