CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FRob said: "This going to go against
OL,8,Ffarming and rural communities.. So all
OL,9,Fthe other parties have jumped in and
OL,10,Fsaid they'll support farmers - but how
OL,11,Fmuch they actually support farmers is
OL,12,Fa different matter."
OL,14,FTo save money, the couple have swapped
OL,15,Fout heating oil for an air-source pump
OL,16,Fand installed solar panels.
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
