OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FTheir farm is along the popular North
OL,8,FCoast 500 driving route. The recent
OL,9,Fspike in fuel prices at the pumps has
OL,10,Fmeant the motorhome site for tourists
OL,11,Fis not seeing as many campers as they
OL,12,Fnormally would at this time of year.
OL,14,F"It's been a lot quieter, the
OL,15,Fweather's been great, we should be
OL,16,Ffull," Emma said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
