CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,F"We have two or three (campervans)
OL,8,Fwhen we should have five or six. We
OL,9,Fhave lots of texts from potential
OL,10,Fbookers asking 'What's fuel prices?
OL,11,FHave you got fuel?'"
OL,13,FLorraine and Peter, from Kent,
OL,14,Fregularly visit the site but the cost
OL,15,Fof diesel, which peaked at over #2 per
OL,16,Flitre recently, has forced them to
OL,17,Fchange their travel plans and mind
OL,18,Ftheir budget.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@WpmoD@bpnsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
