PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FLorraine said: "The cost of fuel has
OL,8,Fchanged how we do things. Normally
OL,9,Fwe'd go back and forth across the east
OL,10,For west coast of the Highlands based
OL,11,Fon where the weather is best but now,
OL,12,Fwe've just stuck to the shorter routes
OL,13,Fand saved money."
OL,15,FIt's not just those reliant on
OL,16,Ffarmland who are feeling the pinch.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
