PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FAndrea, who works with the trust
OL,8,Fdoesn't feel hopeful that a new
OL,9,FScottish Government will provide
OL,10,Frelief from the hardships of the cost
OL,11,Fof living.
OL,13,FShe said: "Are we all going to be in
OL,14,Fthis situation where you can't afford
OL,15,Fto heat your house? You can't afford
OL,16,Fto eat proper food? I can't see that
OL,17,Fit's going to get any better, I don't
OL,18,Fknow where it's all going to end."
OL,26,@uD@KOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
