OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FA familiar rallying call for support
OL,8,Fis that of the hospitality industry,
OL,9,Fwhich through economic hardships and
OL,10,Fthe consequences of the pandemic has
OL,11,Foften struggled to tread water.
OL,13,FAll of that compounded with the cost
OL,14,Fof running a restaurant in an isolated
OL,15,Fpart of the country, the owner of The
OL,16,FAngry Seagull fish and chip shop says
OL,17,Fit's becoming harder not to pass the
OL,18,Fcosts on to customers - with the real
OL,19,Fterms price of a single meal nearing
OL,20,F#20
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FWithin weeks of opening a new shop the
OL,8,Fcost of wholesale fish doubled.
OL,10,FGrant MacNicol, chef and owner, said:
OL,11,F"Fish and chips should be that
OL,12,Faffordable commodity, where you can go
OL,13,Fon a fishy Friday. Now it's getting to
OL,14,Fthe point where not everyone can
OL,15,Fafford it. It's a real shame for the
OL,16,Findustry.
OL,18,F"You can't turn around to the customer
OL,19,Fand say you're now paying #18 for fish
OL,20,Fand chips, they're just not gonna buy
OL,21,Fit."
OL,26,@sD@AOU}D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FOn top of the hike in produce costs,
OL,8,FGrant's business has also been hit
OL,9,Fwith rising fuel prices, which he says
OL,10,Fhave doubled the cost for him to take
OL,11,Fhis mobile fish & chip van on the road
OL,12,Fto draw in customers from further
OL,13,Fafield.
OL,15,FAlong with the SNP's promise to make
OL,16,Fgrocery shopping cheaper by capping
OL,17,Fprices, other parties have also
OL,18,Fpledged to tackle the cost of living.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
