PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778029387
OL,3,CNext Scottish government needs to
OL,4,Ctackle cost of living, say Highland
OL,5,Cvoters
OL,7,FScottish Labour, the Scottish
OL,8,FConservatives and Reform UK Scotland
OL,9,Fsay they'll cut taxes.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Liberal Democrats and
OL,12,FScottish Greens plan to help heat
OL,13,Fhomes to bring down energy bills.
OL,15,FIt takes a lot of dedication to keep
OL,16,Fhouseholds in rural Scotland running.
OL,18,FThis community wants the next Scottish
OL,19,Fgovernment to show them that they care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
